page5.content: This website is made by Scrum Team Women in STEM with members Pranavi Inukurti, Shraddha Kadaba, Meena Annamalai, and Madhumita Narayan. Scrum Team 5 . Team Roles: Scrum Master is Pranavi Inukurti Deployment Manager is Madhumita Narayan Backend Developer is Meena Annamalai Frontend Developer is Shraddha Kadaba .
